          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We often repair Maytag stove problems such as:</p>
            <ul>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Burners not lighting or heating</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Oven not reaching or maintaining set temperature</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Uneven baking or roasting</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Stove shutting off during operation</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Control panel or display not working</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Error codes</strong> like F1, F3, or F9</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Broken or cracked glass cooktop</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Strange odors or gas smell</strong></li>
