            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">We use only <strong>genuine Maytag parts</strong> to ensure safety, compatibility, and long-lasting performance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-5">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
