          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We provide honest, brand-specific advice:</p>
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <li><strong>Repair</strong> – If your stove is under 15 years old, well-maintained, and the repair cost is less than half the price of replacement</li>
              <li><strong>Replace</strong> – If it's older, has recurring issues, or needs multiple costly parts</li>
            </ul>

